on\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Jan 18, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iyp1705578237127.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iyp1705578237127.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iyp1705578237127.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iie1665702850520\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                             \n Menu Item Triggers\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iie1665702850520__section_w3840ab1b5b1_w3841ab1b5_w3842ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Menu Triggers</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Trigger</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Available On</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">Description</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ckm1665702665911.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ckm1665702665911.html\" title=\"System trigger that is executed before a menu or menu item is displayed.\">trigger preDisplay</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Option\n Dynamic menu\n Cascading menu\n Separator\n Drop-down menu Right Align Marker</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">The preDisplay trigger is activated before a menu is displayed.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can control if and how the menu item is displayed using the ProcScript functions <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$hide</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$disable</span>, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$check</span>, and <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$inlinemenu</span>, which are only available in this trigger.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can use the preDisplay trigger to set or return values and to specify if an item is available. For example, you can use the preDisplay trigger, to enable or disable the item, or to check or uncheck it depending on the current state of the application.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"eji1665703130687.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eji1665703130687.html\" title=\"Trigger for handling the processing that should occur after a menu item is selected.\">trigger option</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Option</p>\n<p class=\"p\">Dynamic menu</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"iie1665702850520__d6410e17__entry__3\">\n<p class=\"p\">The option trigger is activated when the user clicks the menu item or presses the shortcut key.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">You can use the option trigger to program an action, such as activating a form.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eoe1705578839705.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>ProcScript for Menus</a><p>You control how a menu item is displayed by using the ProcScript instructions in the preDisplay trigger.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5828882\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_5828882\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Menu Item Triggers Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Jan 18, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Menu Item Triggers Menu items have associated triggers in which to program the conditions under which they are displayed and the action they perform. Table 1. Menu Triggers Trigger Available On Description trigger preDisplay Option Dynamic menu Cascading menu Separator Drop-down menu Right Align Marker The preDisplay trigger is activated before a menu is displayed. You can control if and how the menu item is displayed using the ProcScript functions $hide , $disable , $check , and $inlinemenu , which are only available in this trigger. You can use the preDisplay trigger to set or return values and to specify if an item is available. For example, you can use the preDisplay trigger, to enable or disable the item, or to check or uncheck it depending on the current state of the application. trigger option Option Dynamic menu The option trigger is activated when the user clicks the menu item or presses the shortcut key. You can use the option trigger to program an action, such as activating a form. Related Links ProcScript for Menus You control how a menu item is displayed by using the ProcScript instructions in the preDisplay trigger. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}